# Our Date Map - PWA Project Context

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js (App Router, TypeScript)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Backend/DB: Supabase (PostgreSQL, Storage)
- Map API: Kakao Maps JavaScript API
- PWA: Standalone mode optimization, browser-image-compression

## Coding Rules & Vibe Coding Principles
1. Always write clean, fully typed TypeScript code.
2. Mobile-first responsive design using Tailwind CSS.
3. Optimize images below 300KB using `browser-image-compression` before uploading to Supabase Storage.
4. Keep full-screen map layout without scrollbars (PWA app-like UI).